lead_paragraph: Lawyers for a man in prison for killing basketball star Michael Jordan's father 23 years ago say they found more evidence of police misconduct that clears him in the shooting.

headline.main: Man in Jail for Killing Jordan's Dad Makes Misconduct Claim
